data.description: Seller has put new roof, walls, floors, windows, doors, cabinets, and bathroom during his ownership. Home has 2 bedrooms, 1 Bath, Kitchen, Living Room, Dining Room, and extra room that used to be the 3rd bedroom. Living room is large with an awesome view out the bay window. Kitchen was remodeled to add many cabinets and counter top. Seller is wanting to leave some items, to include Refrigerator, Stove, microwave, dishwasher, trash compactor, washer and dryer. Seller will be taking the Living Room TV but is leaving the wall mount. You will love the 20x40 metal out building. Seller may be leaving some small tools. You will love the location and the convenience of this place! Seller is wanting to sell as is but will try and work with any qualified buyer.
